  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1060",
  "title": "searchBox upgrade",
  "body": "- should have good behavior by default: http://shipow.github.io/searchbox/\n- container: should be possible to use a `<div>` container: we create the whole markup\n- should be possible to bind an existing `<input>`\n- should be possible to link to a wrapping `<form>` so that we listen for `submit` and `reset` events\n- remove searchOnlyOnEnterKey\n- add searchAsYouType\n- remove poweredBy, poweredBy is a simple link below the input, there's no need to have it by default in the widget\n- should embed default shortcuts to focus: ['s', '/']\n\nprevious discussion #859\n",
